[SPEAKER_09]: Victor, thank you for all your work.

55
00:05:47,867 --> 00:05:48,587
[SPEAKER_09]: We appreciate it.

56
00:05:48,607 --> 00:05:54,851
[SPEAKER_09]: But again, I need to show my displeasure in the fact that this isn't hurting us right now.

57
