[SPEAKER_04]: Councillor Carvillo.

179
00:19:25,808 --> 00:19:27,370
[SPEAKER_08]: some of the permits that we did over the years.

180
00:19:27,390 --> 00:19:29,293
[SPEAKER_08]: Most of the time we approved permits.

181
00:19:29,333 --> 00:19:30,374
[SPEAKER_08]: These people never even showed up.

182
00:19:31,996 --> 00:19:35,140
[SPEAKER_08]: And then I've gone to many events, and there's food trucks there.

183
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:37,403
